This is the introduction to learn Angular and Wep API while creating an application named property selling application
  Angular topics include
  1) Project Setup
  2) Basics
  3) Binding
  4) Bootstrap
  5) Components 
  6) Interaction between components
  7) Using Service
  8) Routing
  9) Template Driven Forms
  10) Reactive Forms
  11) Inbuilt Validation
  12) Custom Validation
  13) Photo Gallery
  14) Observable and Resolver
  15) Save Data to local storage
  16) pipes
  17) Lazy Loading
  18) Authentication
  19) Upload image
  20) Deployment on Firebase
  Finally angular and web api integration through .net core
  
